data.name: textBox18.Text
data.value: The Beauty Products category encompasses a wide range of items dedicated to enhancing and maintaining one's physical appearance. It includes a diverse array of products designed for skincare, makeup, hair care, and personal fragrance.

data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: In the Personal Care category, you will find products like soaps, shampoos, conditioners, body washes, and toothpaste, which are essential for daily hygiene. Cleanse, nourish, and protect the body's skin and hair with these products.

data.name: textBox21.Text
data.value: Within the Household Essentials category, you will find products such as storage containers, bins, and baskets. These items help with organizing and storing various items, allowing for efficient use of space and keeping the home tidy.

data.name: textBox15.Text
data.value: Cleaning Supplies include items such as multi-purpose cleaners, disinfectants, and sanitizers. Surfaces such as countertops, floors, appliances, and fixtures can be effectively cleaned with these products. Clean and sanitized environments reduce the risk of spreading illnesses and promote overall hygiene.
